c: 41
v: 45
t: "wlqd atayna musaa altawrat kama ataynak -ayha alrswl- alquran fa'akhtalif fiha qwmh: faminhum man amn, waminhum man kdhdhab. walawla kalimat sabaqat min rabik bitajil aleadhab ean qawmik lfusil baynahum b'ihlak alkafirin fi alhal, wa'iin almushrikin lafi shakin min alquran shadid alrybt"